spec_data.Name: texlive-rcs-multi
spec_data.Description:
The package enables the user to typeset version control
information provided by RCS keywords (e.g., $ID: ... $) in
LaTeX documents that contain multiple TeX files. The package is
based on the author's svn-multi package.
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Sun 06 Aug 2017 07:49:23 AM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: Typeset RCS version control in multiple-file documents
